title: My Top 6 Android P Features
tags: Android P: Top 6 things you need to know!
The biggest early visual changes in Android P
description:
One of the perks of having a Pixel is you get to try the latest Android version. Android P is out, and here are my top 6 features. 

Notch
Ringer Volume
Screenshot and Edit
Auto Rotate
Adaptive brightness
Permission
